titles.title: Electing certain Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

term.name: House Committee on Education and the Workforce

bill.summary: 5/29/2014--Passed House without amendment. Elects specified Members to the following House Committees: (1) Education and the Workforce, and (2) Foreign Affairs.
